values: list cut, since i no longer will be using this journal for its original purpose, but am too fond of the name to let it go to waste. absolutely no hard feelings at all -- if you were here, you know you are loved -- but i'm going to be using it for something else now, so i decided to cut the journal down to only those in some way involved. if you ever need to see an old post here, just let me know and i'll dig it out, but otherwise, you know where to find me. :) thank you all so much! i love you guys.
